üêé Rampante
================================================
A fancy and opinionated nanoframework for microservices.


The name
================================================

Rampante means "rampant" in Italian.

Why Kafka?
================================================

I like aiokafka, but I plan to switch to Redis as soon as `Stream` will be officially available.

